<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Allegiance" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Allegiance,</orth> fidelity of subjects, loyalty: <cit><quote>to follow with a. a fall'n lord,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 3.13.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 13, 44</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>contrary to the faith and a. of a true subject,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 2, 20</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ado 3.3.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 3, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 3.1.175" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 1, 175</bibl> <cit><quote>(to one).</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 2.1.108" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 1, 108</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r2 3.3.37" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.2.4" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 2, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.5.3" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 5, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.1.70" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 1, 70</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.7.19" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 7, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.171" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 171</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.2.62" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 2, 62</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.43" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.1.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 1, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.131" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 5, 131</bibl>. <cit><quote>I charge thee on thy a.:</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 1.1.210" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 1, 210</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ado 1.1.210" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 1, 210</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wt 2.3.121" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 3, 121</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.1.86" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 1, 86</bibl> <cit><quote>(on a. to ourself).</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 1.1.170" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 1, 170</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to swear a. to one:</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 5.1.10" default="NO" valid="yes">John V, 1, 10</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.169" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 4, 169</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.20" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B V, 1, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.20" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B V, 1, 20</bibl><lb />Devotion in general: <cit><quote>pluck a. from men's hearts,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.2.52" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 2, 52</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>